This program uses CMake as its build system.

Build Requirements:
cmake >= 3.8
ncurses-dev >= 5
C++ toolchain (GCC and Clang have been tested)
jq >= 1.5 | python >= 3
sh-compatible shell

Build Steps:

Out-of-source build (recommended)
mkdir build && cd build && cmake .. && cmake --build .

In-source build
cmake . && cmake --build .
